5' x 6.6' | Collapsible Blue/Green Screen
Description:
The 5 x 6.6', blue/green Collapsible Reversible Background from Neewer has a foldable and portable design supporting bidirectional mounting and a wide range of applications. It allows quick and clean chroma key compositing in videos and images, ideal for vlogging, broadcasting, gaming, portrait/product photography, and more. A pop-up backdrop allows setup in just a few seconds. The double-sided design provides green and blue screens for more flexibility.

Three loops let you hang the backdrop on a stand, curtain rod, or wall hooks in vertical or horizontal directions for different camera distances. The background easily folds into a compact circle and stores in the included carry bag. Steel frames bend and twist easily, letting you fold the backdrop down to a 24.8" compact round shape.
